Name: CERVICAL INTRAEPITHELIAL NEOPLASIA GRADE 1
Description: The least risky type of cervical intraepithelial neoplasia, this represents only mild dysplasia, or abnormal cell growth.  It is confined to the basal 1/3 of the epithelium.

CIN 1

Name: CERVICAL INTRAEPITHELIAL NEOPLASIA GRADE 2
